additionalCredentialsWarning.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-SPHttp] Message to show the end user when additional credentials are required to access restricted information.
additionalCredentialsWarning.value: Additional credentials are required to show this page correctly.

servicePrincipalNotAvaliableError.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-SPHttp] Message to show when SharePoint Online Web Application Service Principal is not available in this tenant.
servicePrincipalNotAvaliableError.value: The SharePoint Online Web Application Service Principal hasn't been provisioned yet. Please contact your Tenant Administrator.

graphClientInitializationError.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-SPHttp] Message to show when the MSGraphClient cannot be constructed. MSGraphClient is a javascript SDK for interacting with Microsoft Graph's REST APIs.
graphClientInitializationError.value: MSGraphClient cannot be constructed due to an unknown failure
